core:processNote.core:description: For Payment Module input, we first try to load the exact equivalent IIN range as the Payment Module, but if that fails we will try to find a, enclosing IIN range given the returned PAN IIN and PAN Length.

Input must have one of: CardDataEvent (from Payment Module), CardTrack2 (from non-PM MSR), CardReadEvent (non-PM ICC reader) or CardNumberKeyed. If non-pm ICC, then ICCTransactiondata must be supplied as well.

core:action.core:comment: Test incoming card data event for error
